title: Love Story (Ana and Ryan's Version)
description:
A big congrats is in order for Ana and her fiance, Ryan! Hear all about how he gave Ana the surprise of a lifetime when he pulled off this incredible proposal! And Taylor, if you're listening, we need something from you!
What ways can we incorporate this into the podcast? What should Ana pick for her wedding songs? What's your favorite love song by Taylor Swift? There are lots of ways to reach us.. and make sure to congrats our blushing bride-to-be!
